{"tid":783332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雅加達亞運】港迷打氣被中國龍之隊辱罵 港足達標逼和巴勒斯坦","createTime":"2018-08-17T12:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T12:33:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc28d6b236d54a3288066ba37262d838acdda90f","tid":783332,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180817/large/1534502476_65be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180817%2Flarge%2F1534502476_65be.jpg&h=19d2319f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「香港力量」成員恆仔，今天來到球場支持港足對巴勒斯坦的亞運分組賽，但球賽開始不久，一班大約20人的中國龍之隊球迷靠近，並和恆仔發生爭執，當中更有人以粗口「傻X」辱罵恆仔。其後因為雙方仍有爭執，所以恆仔被調至另一區觀看比賽。恆仔賽後表示，中國和印尼球迷帶入場的橫額均無問題，但其「香港力量」banner就不准掛上，極感不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180817/large/1534500411_c27f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180817%2Flarge%2F1534500411_c27f.jpg&h=46bc30d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【香港1:1巴勒斯坦】<br />\n全場完！香港憑下半場林嘉緯的入球，以1:1賽和上半場領先的巴勒斯坦。港隊在上半場中主導形勢，但被反擊銳利的巴軍先入一球；在下半場，港隊有較多具威脅的埋門，終憑林嘉緯在57分鐘接應樂仔右路的傳中球射入。而香港較後時間亦有佐迪入球，但可惜傳球的鍾偉強越位在先。現時港隊賽和巴勒斯坦後，三戰兩勝一和的七分，出線形勢樂觀，暫以一分落後多賽一場的巴勒斯坦排在次席，下場將在20號面對有主場優勢的印尼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180817/58575106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58575106&d=gymw88FKLZleXhCH8leI0jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=416225f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58575106&h=089dbe8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180817/58575106</a>"}]}